H0.text: What kind of bird is the Ugly Duckling. Goose

H1.text: What kind of bird is the Ugly Duckling. Pochard

H2.text: What kind of bird is the Ugly Duckling. Merganser

H3.text: What kind of bird is the Ugly Duckling. Swan

A4.text: He had been not a duckling but a cygnet all this time.

A5.text: He decides to throw himself at a flock of swans, feeling that it is better to be killed by such beautiful birds than to live a life of ugliness.
